interval = 95
q = interval/200 + 0.5
k = 10000
mu = mean(sample_zero1) - mean(sample_zero2)
test = t.test(sample_zero1, sample_zero2)
tval = as.numeric(test$statistic)
se = mu/tval
df = as.numeric(test$parameter)
CI = qt(q, df)
